'''染料敏化太阳能电池'''（dye-sensitized solar cell，缩写为'''DSSC'''、'''DSC''' 或'''DYSC'''<ref>Haiying Wan, [http://bama.ua.edu/~chem/seminars/student_seminars/fall04/papers-f04/wan-sem.pdf "Dye Sensitized Solar Cells"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060911115045/http://bama.ua.edu/~chem/seminars/student_seminars/fall04/papers-f04/wan-sem.pdf |date=2006-09-11 }}, University of Alabama Department of Chemistry, p. 3</ref>）是一种廉价的[[薄膜太阳能电池|薄膜太阳能电池]]。<ref>[http://www.eifer.uni-karlsruhe.de/162.php "Dye-Sensitized vs. Thin Film Solar Cells"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060210233608/http://www.eifer.uni-karlsruhe.de/162.php |date=2006-02-10 }}, European Institute for Energy Research, 30 June 2006</ref>它是基于由光敏电极和电解质构成的半导体，是一个[[光化学电池|电气化学系统]]。这种电池的一种较新的版本——也叫做[[格雷策尔电池|格雷策尔电池]]，是由[[米夏埃尔·格雷策尔|米夏埃尔·格雷策尔]]（Michael Grätzel）和布赖恩·奥勒冈1991年在[[洛桑联邦理工学院|洛桑联邦理工学院]]发明的。<ref>
{{cite journal|author = Brian O'Regan, Michael Grätzel
|title = A low-cost, high-efficiency solar cell based on dye-sensitized colloidal TiO<sub>2</sub> films
|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_nature-uk_1991-10-24_353_6346/page/737
|journal = Nature
|volume = 353|issue = 6346
|pages = 737–740|date = 24 October 1991
|doi = 10.1038/353737a0|bibcode = 1991Natur.353..737O }}</ref>米夏埃尔·格雷策尔尔因为本发明而曾荣获2010年[[千禧年科技獎|千禧年科技獎]]（2010 millennium technology grand prize）。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20100613065310/http://www.millenniumprize.fi/news/165/111/PROFESSOR-GRaeTZEL-WINS-THE-2010-MILLENNIUM-TECHNOLOGY-GRAND-PRIZE-FOR-DYE-SENSITIZED-SOLAR-CELLS/d%2Cnews_en/ Professor Grätzel wins the 2010 millennium technology grand prize for dye-sensitized solar cells], Technology Academy Finland, 14 June 2010.</ref>

具有许多吸引人的特征; 因为它可以用低廉的材料制成（但实际中已经证明它很难摆脱对于贵重金属[[铂|铂]]和[[钌|钌]]的限制，并且它的液态的电极对于各种天气的适应也是一个严重挑战），不需要用精细的仪器来制造，这种电池在技术上很有吸引力。而且，其制造过程比以前的电晶体电池要便宜。它可以被制成软片，机械强度大，不需要特别保护就可以防护树枝或者冰雹的撞击。虽然它的[[能量转换效率|能量转换效率]]比最好的薄膜电池要低，但理论上它们的[[性价比|性价比]]已足够高，在完成[[市电平价|市电平价]]的情况下可以与[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]相提并论。由于化学稳定性问题而被搁置的商业应用<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1016/j.ccr.2004.05.030|title=Dye sensitization solar cells: a critical assessment of the learning curve|year=2004|last1=Tributsch|first1=H|journal=Coordination Chemistry Reviews|volume=248|issue=13–14|pages=1511–1530}}</ref>, 在{{le|欧盟光伏路线图|European Union Photovoltaic Roadmap}}中预测将在2020年之前显着促进可再生能源发电。

